latestPosts.caption:
✨ Share this with your partner to plan your next soothing date night in Gurgaon!
.
Because this hidden gem is a whole vibe — from the food to the ambiance, everything here screams perfect evening plan 💑🌙

🔹 What we ordered:
🍕 Veg Pizza 
🍜 Hakka Noodles 
🍛 Kadhai Paneer + Dal Makhni
🥖 Served with garma garam Naan 

🔹 What we loved:
🎶 Live music even on weekdays
💡 Dreamy lights & aesthetic corners
📸 Instagrammable setups for cute couple clicks

🔹 Pro tips before you go:
🚗 Take your own car – cab struggle is real on Gwal Pahadi Road
🌃 Go for dinner, the vibe is way better in the evening
📍 Save this café for your next special evening out!

✨ Tag your partner, save this post, and follow me for more luxury & travel gems around the city!

This viral BYOB in Gurgaon is all hype, no experience.
.
Here’s the real tea:
– 1K entry, only 500 redeemable 
– Bees all over the outdoor area
– Extra charges for prime seats
– Half the menu unavailable
– Food = bland, overpriced
– Too crowded on weekends
It’s good for pics, but a hard NO for the experience.
Would you still go here? Or have you been already? Let’s talk in the comments!
